The best things in life often come after the longest wait... This speaks for so many things in my life. Pursuing my dreams, all with adventures and my work continue to grow my patience every day. Like the Grand Canyon having been on my bucket list since I was little, also finally getting my puppy @timber_tails üê∂, who has brought nothing but joy to my life. The timing was finally right. I have wanted a dog for ever and if I had got one sooner I wouldn't have him! I'll also be headed back to school in the fall for my teaching degree and this decision rose due to all the situations and adventures that had occurred in my life thus far... life is crazy but I wouldn't change a single thing about it. Also wishing I was back here right now! Thanks @andyaustinphoto for helping me out with this shot! #freshairandfreedom #grandcanyon
